sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser as Browser (React SPA)
    participant Server as Express Server
    participant S3 as AWS S3 Storage
    participant Claude as Claude 3.5 Sonnet
    participant DB as MySQL Database
    participant OAuth as Manus OAuth

    Note over User,OAuth: Authentication Flow
    User->>Browser: Visit platform
    Browser->>Server: GET /api/trpc/auth.me
    Server->>DB: Query user by session cookie
    DB-->>Server: User record or null
    Server-->>Browser: User state

    Note over User,Claude: AI Analysis Flow
    User->>Browser: Fill player form + select file
    Browser->>Browser: Extract base64 from image/video frame
    Browser->>Server: POST /api/scout/upload {fileData, mimeType}
    Server->>Server: Buffer.from(base64)
    Server->>S3: storagePut(key, buffer, mimeType)
    S3-->>Server: {url: CDN_URL, key: S3_KEY}
    Server-->>Browser: {url: CDN_URL}

    Browser->>Server: POST /api/scout/analyze {imageUrl, playerInfo}
    Server->>Server: Build FIFA/SAFF prompt
    Server->>Claude: generateText({image: URL, text: prompt})
    Note over Server,Claude: ~8 seconds response time
    Claude-->>Server: JSON scout report (25 fields)
    Server->>Server: Parse + validate JSON
    Server-->>Browser: {success: true, report: AIScoutReport}
    Browser->>Browser: Render full scout report

    Note over User,OAuth: Login Flow (Optional)
    User->>Browser: Click login
    Browser->>OAuth: Redirect to OAuth portal
    OAuth-->>Browser: Redirect with auth code
    Browser->>Server: GET /api/oauth/callback?code=X
    Server->>OAuth: Exchange code for user info
    OAuth-->>Server: User profile
    Server->>DB: Upsert user record
    Server-->>Browser: Set JWT session cookie
